title: Statement by Fianna Fáil Justice Spokesperson on Louth Shooting (Fianna Fáil)
text: ( Source : Fianna Fáil ) Fianna Fáil Spokesperson on Justice Niall Collins has expressed shock and sadness at news of a fatal shooting in County Louth this evening which has claimed the life of a member of An Garda Siochána . Deputy Collins
